&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#1f497d;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;&quot;&gt;Being a creative in the Cat-5 tornado that is an advertising agency is a turbulent life. Here&amp;rsquo;s a quick list of five Chrome browser extensions that will help your day-to-day workflow. Not using Chrome, you say? What&amp;rsquo;s wrong with you. &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.google.com/chrome/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Go download Chrome..&lt;/a&gt; And then install these extensions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

